{"id":151,"parent_id":110,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":151,"title":"Alma 41","subtitle":"","short_title":"Alma","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 41"],[".studySummary",["i","In the Resurrection men come forth to a state of endless happiness or endless misery—Wickedness never was happiness—Carnal men are without God in the world—Every person receives again in the Restoration the characteristics and attributes acquired in mortality. About 74",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.1","order":"05.20.041.16664"},["b","1"],"And now, my son, I have somewhat to say concerning the restoration of which has been spoken; for behold, some have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"wrested"],"the scriptures, and have gone far",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"astray"],"because of this thing. And I perceive that thy mind has been",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"worried"],"also concerning this thing. But behold, I will explain it unto thee."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.2","order":"05.20.041.16665"},["b","2"],"I say unto thee, my son, that the plan of restoration is requisite with the justice of God; for it is requisite that all things should be restored to their proper order. Behold, it is requisite and just, according to the power and resurrection of Christ, that the soul of man should be restored to its body, and that every",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"part"],"of the body should be restored to itself."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.3","order":"05.20.041.16666"},["b","3"],"And it is requisite with the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"justice"],"of God that men should be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"judged"],"according to their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"works"],"; and if their works were good in this life, and the desires of their hearts were good, that they should also, at the last day, be",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"restored"],"unto that which is good."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.4","order":"05.20.041.16667"},["b","4"],"And if their works are evil they shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"restored"],"unto them for evil. Therefore, all things shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"restored"],"to their proper order, every thing to its natural frame—",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"mortality"],"raised to",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"immortality"],",",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_4e"},"corruption"],"to incorruption—raised to",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_4f"},"endless"],"happiness to",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_4g"},"inherit"],"the kingdom of God, or to endless misery to inherit the kingdom of the devil, the one on one hand, the other on the other—"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.5","order":"05.20.041.16668"},["b","5"],"The one raised to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"happiness"],"according to his desires of happiness, or good according to his desires of good; and the other to evil according to his desires of evil; for as he has desired to do evil all the day long even so shall he have his reward of evil when the night cometh."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.6","order":"05.20.041.16669"},["b","6"],"And so it is on the other hand. If he hath repented of his sins, and desired righteousness until the end of his days, even so he shall be rewarded unto righteousness."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.7","order":"05.20.041.16670"},["b","7"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"These"],"are they that are redeemed of the Lord; yea, these are they that are taken out, that are delivered from that endless night of darkness; and thus they stand or fall; for behold, they are their own",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"judges"],", whether to do good or do evil."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.8","order":"05.20.041.16671"},["b","8"],"Now, the decrees of God are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"unalterable"],"; therefore, the way is prepared that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"whosoever"],"will may",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"walk"],"therein and be saved."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.9","order":"05.20.041.16672"},["b","9"],"And now behold, my son, do not risk",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"one"],"more offense against your God upon those points of doctrine, which ye have hitherto risked to commit sin."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.10","order":"05.20.041.16673"},["b","10"],"Do not suppose, because it has been spoken concerning restoration, that ye shall be restored from sin to happiness. Behold, I say unto you,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"wickedness"],"never was",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"happiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.11","order":"05.20.041.16674"},["b","11"],"And now, my son, all men that are in a state of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"nature"],", or I would say, in a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"carnal"],"state, are in the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"gall of bitterness"],"and in the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"bonds"],"of iniquity; they are",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_11e"},"without"],"God in the world, and they have gone",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_11f"},"contrary"],"to the nature of God; therefore, they are in a state contrary to the nature of happiness."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.12","order":"05.20.041.16675"},["b","12"],"And now behold, is the meaning of the word restoration to take a thing of a natural state and place it in an unnatural state, or to place it in a state opposite to its nature?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.13","order":"05.20.041.16676"},["b","13"],"O, my son, this is not the case; but the meaning of the word restoration is to bring back again",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"evil"],"for evil, or carnal for carnal, or devilish for devilish—good for that which is good; righteous for that which is righteous; just for that which is just; merciful for that which is merciful."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.14","order":"05.20.041.16677"},["b","14"],"Therefore, my son, see that you are merciful unto your brethren; deal",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"justly"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"judge"],"righteously, and do",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"good"],"continually; and if ye do all these things then shall ye receive your",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"reward"],"; yea, ye shall have",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_14e"},"mercy"],"restored unto you again; ye shall have justice restored unto you again; ye shall have a righteous judgment restored unto you again; and ye shall have good rewarded unto you again."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.15","order":"05.20.041.16678"},["b","15"],"For that which ye do",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"send"],"out shall return unto you again, and be restored; therefore, the word restoration more fully condemneth the sinner, and justifieth him not at all."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.1a","order":"05.20.041.16679"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/1.20"},"2 Pet. 1:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.16"},"3:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/13.20"},"Alma 13:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.1b","order":"05.20.041.16681"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-individuals"},"TG Apostasy of Individuals"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.1c","order":"05.20.041.16683"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/problem-solving"},"TG Problem-Solving"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.2a","order":"05.20.041.16685"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/40.23"},"Alma 40:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.3a","order":"05.20.041.16687"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-justice-of"},"TG God, Justice of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/justice"},"Justice"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.3b","order":"05.20.041.16689"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/accountability"},"TG Accountability"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/judgment-the-last"},"Judgment, the Last"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.3c","order":"05.20.041.16691"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/59.18"},"Isa. 59:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/36.15"},"Alma 36:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.27"},"42:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.10.9-10"},"D&C 1:10 (9–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.3d","order":"05.20.041.16693"},["b","3d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/14.31"},"Hel. 14:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.4a","order":"05.20.041.16695"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.28"},"Alma 42:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.4b","order":"05.20.041.16697"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.13.10-13"},"2 Ne. 9:13 (10–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/138.17"},"D&C 138:17"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/resurrection"},"TG Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.4c","order":"05.20.041.16699"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mortality"},"TG Mortality"],"."],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.4d","order":"05.20.041.16701"},["b","4d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/immortality"},"TG Immortality"],"."],["div",{"id":"4e","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.4e","order":"05.20.041.16703"},["b","4e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/15.50.50-53"},"1 Cor. 15:50 (50–53)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4f","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.4f","order":"05.20.041.16705"},["b","4f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/eternal-life"},"TG Eternal Life"],"."],["div",{"id":"4g","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.4g","order":"05.20.041.16707"},["b","4g"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/exaltation"},"TG Exaltation"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.5a","order":"05.20.041.16709"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/happiness"},"TG Happiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.7a","order":"05.20.041.16711"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.65"},"D&C 76:65"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.7b","order":"05.20.041.16713"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.26"},"2 Ne. 2:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.27"},"Alma 42:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/14.30"},"Hel. 14:30"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/agency"},"TG Agency"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.8a","order":"05.20.041.16715"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/9.19"},"Morm. 9:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.8b","order":"05.20.041.16717"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.27"},"Alma 42:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.8c","order":"05.20.041.16719"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.9a","order":"05.20.041.16721"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/26.11"},"Prov. 26:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/12.45.43-45"},"Matt. 12:45 (43–45)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.26.23-28"},"D&C 42:26 (23–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.10a","order":"05.20.041.16723"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/32.10"},"Ps. 32:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/57.21"},"Isa. 57:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.38"},"Hel. 13:38"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/evil"},"TG Evil"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wickedness"},"Wickedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.10b","order":"05.20.041.16725"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/50.21"},"Alma 50:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/2.13"},"Morm. 2:13"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/happiness"},"TG Happiness"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace-of-god"},"Peace of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.11a","order":"05.20.041.16727"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.19"},"Mosiah 3:19"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-natural-not-spiritually-reborn"},"TG Man, Natural, Not Spiritually Reborn"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.11b","order":"05.20.041.16729"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/carnal-mind"},"TG Carnal Mind"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fall-of-man"},"Fall of Man"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.11c","order":"05.20.041.16731"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/8.23"},"Acts 8:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/8.31"},"Morm. 8:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"11d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.11d","order":"05.20.041.16733"},["b","11d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bondage-spiritual"},"TG Bondage, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"11e","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.11e","order":"05.20.041.16735"},["b","11e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/2.12"},"Eph. 2:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27.31"},"Mosiah 27:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"11f","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.11f","order":"05.20.041.16737"},["b","11f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.38"},"Hel. 13:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.13a","order":"05.20.041.16739"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/12.10"},"Dan. 12:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/22.12.6-16"},"Rev. 22:12 (6–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.14a","order":"05.20.041.16741"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honesty"},"TG Honesty"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.14b","order":"05.20.041.16743"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/7.1.1-5"},"Matt. 7:1 (1–5)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/11.12"},"D&C 11:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.14c","order":"05.20.041.16745"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/benevolence"},"TG Benevolence"],"."],["div",{"id":"14d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.14d","order":"05.20.041.16747"},["b","14d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reward"},"TG Reward"],"."],["div",{"id":"14e","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.14e","order":"05.20.041.16749"},["b","14e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mercy"},"TG Mercy"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.15a","order":"05.20.041.16751"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/19.17"},"Prov. 19:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/11.1"},"Eccl. 11:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.27.27-28"},"Alma 42:27 (27–28)"],"."]]}
